[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]於2013年12月確認開始電影製作<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Fox Remaking ‘Murder on the Orient Express’ (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/fox-remaking-murder-on-the-orient-express-exclusive-1200950073/|accessdate=2015-11-25|work=Variety|date=2013-12-12|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125153117/https://variety.com/2013/film/news/fox-remaking-murder-on-the-orient-express-exclusive-1200950073/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年6月16日，福斯聘請[[肯尼斯·布萊納|肯尼斯·布萊納]]擔任導演，執導一部改編自《[[東方快車謀殺案|東方快車謀殺案]]》的新電影<ref>{{cite web|last1=Geier|first1=Thom|title=Kenneth Branagh in Talks to Direct Agatha Christie’s ‘Murder on the Orient Express’ (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/kenneth-branagh-in-talks-to-direct-agatha-christie-murder-on-the-orient-express-exclusive/|website=TheWrap|date=2015-06-16|accessdate=2015-07-11|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308142544/https://www.thewrap.com/kenneth-branagh-in-talks-to-direct-agatha-christie-murder-on-the-orient-express-exclusive/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年11月20日，宣布布萊納將在電影中飾演偵探[[赫丘勒·白羅|赫丘勒·白羅]]<ref name=BranaghCast>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=Kenneth Branagh to Direct, Star in ‘Murder on the Orient Express’ Remake|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/kenneth-branagh-star-directing-murder-on-the-orient-express-1201645936/|accessdate=2015-11-25|work=Variety|date=2015-11-20|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111344/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/kenneth-branagh-star-directing-murder-on-the-orient-express-1201645936/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[麥可·葛林_(編劇)|麥可·葛林]]將撰寫劇本。2016年6月10日，據報導，[[安潔莉娜·裘莉|安潔莉娜·裘莉]]將出演電影<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bamigboye|first1=Baz|title=BAZ BAMIGBOYE: Don't miss the train, Angelina|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3634423/BAZ-BAMIGBOYE-Don-t-miss-train-Angelina.html|accessdate=2016-06-12|work=Mail Online|date=2016-06-10|archive-date=2017-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830070823/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3634423/BAZ-BAMIGBOYE-Don-t-miss-train-Angelina.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌於8月4日報導，她將不會成為主演中的一員，而工作室正尋找其他女演員，如[[莎莉·賽隆|莎莉·賽隆]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lang|first1=Brent|title=Angelina Jolie No Longer Boarding ‘Murder on the Orient Express’ (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/angelina-jolie-murder-on-the-orient-express-2-1201830713/|accessdate=2016-08-07|work=Variety|date=2016-08-04|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125140315/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/angelina-jolie-murder-on-the-orient-express-2-1201830713/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月17日，據《綜藝》雜誌指出，{{link-en|小萊斯里·歐多姆|Leslie Odom Jr.}}正談判以未知角色加入劇組<ref>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=‘Hamilton’ Star Leslie Odom Jr. in Talks to Join ‘Murder on the Orient Express’ (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/leslie-odom-jr-murder-on-the-orient-express-1201839535/|accessdate=2016-09-15|work=Variety|date=2016-08-17|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115417/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/leslie-odom-jr-murder-on-the-orient-express-1201839535/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月6日，《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》報導，{{link-en|湯姆·貝特曼|Tom Bateman}} 加盟電影，飾演白羅的同伴及助手柏克，他在東方快車公司工作<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ford|first1=Rebecca|title='Murder on the Orient Express' Adding Tom Bateman (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/murder-orient-express-adding-tom-924733|accessdate=2016-09-15|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-09-06|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122031148/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/murder-orient-express-adding-tom-924733|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月29日，[[強尼·戴普|強尼·戴普]]、[[蜜雪兒·菲佛|蜜雪兒·菲佛]]、[[茱蒂·丹契|茱蒂·丹契]]、[[麥可·潘納|麥可·潘納]]及[[露西·寶通|露西·寶通]]加入演員行列<ref>{{cite news|last2=Kit|first2=Borys|last1=Ford|first1=Rebecca|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/johnny-depp-talks-star-murder-933797|title=Johnny Depp in Talks to Star in 'Murder on the Orient Express'|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-09-29|accessdate=2016-09-30|archive-date=2016-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230191411/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/johnny-depp-talks-star-murder-933797|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|last2=Ford|first2=Rebecca|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michelle-pfeiffer-daisy-ridley-michael-933817|title=Michelle Pfeiffer, Daisy Ridley, Michael Pena, Judi Dench Board 'Murder on the Orient Express' (Exclusive)|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-09-29|accessdate=2016-09-30|archive-date=2017-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170501151826/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/michelle-pfeiffer-daisy-ridley-michael-933817|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[主體攝影|主體攝影]]於2016年11月22日在英國開始<ref>{{cite news|last1=Daniels|first1=Nia|title=Murder on the Orient Express starts filming|url=http://www.theknowledgeonline.com/the-knowledge-bulletin/post/2016/11/22/murder-on-the-orient-express-starts-filming|accessdate=2016-11-22|work=The Knowledge|date=2016-11-22|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225005259/https://www.theknowledgeonline.com/the-knowledge-bulletin/post/2016/11/22/murder-on-the-orient-express-starts-filming|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Daniels|first1=Nia|title=Murder on the Orient Express sets up UK shoot|url=http://www.kftv.com/news/2016/11/15/murder-on-the-orient-express-sets-up-uk-shoot|accessdate=2016-11-22|work=KFTV|date=2016-11-15|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127202358/https://www.kftv.com/news/2016/11/15/murder-on-the-orient-express-sets-up-uk-shoot|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

